---
title: Sweet Chilli Beef Lettuce Cups with Corn Fried Rice
description: Tantalising Asian flavours of garlic, sweet chilli and oyster sauce overflow in these crisp cos lettuce cups! Juicy beef mince is
browned with a medley of spices before layering crunchy veggies, bringing you a bite that packs both unbeatable taste and crunch.
